# migrations/
#
# Why this folder exists:
# Knex migrations are versioned database schema changes stored as timestamped files.
# They allow the entire team to keep their database schema in sync via:
#   npm run migrate
#
# Each migration file exports an `up` function (apply change) and a `down`
# function (rollback). Never edit a migration after it has been run in production.
#
# Generate a new migration:
#   knex migrate:make create_users_table --knexfile src/config/knexfile.js
